headline: Will MACOM (MTSI) Board Addition Sharpen Its AI and 5G Competitive Edge?
summary: MACOM Technology Solutions Holdings, Inc. recently appointed veteran semiconductor executive Bryan Ingram as an independent director to its Board, effective January 12, 2026, bringing experience leading multi-billion-dollar wireless semiconductor businesses at Broadcom, Avago, Agilent and other technology companies.
